3.2.1 Update - Removed 'magic' type convert from view items - Removed OnPropertyChanged, OnErrorChanged, OnItemChanged in view items - Made NotifyPropertyChange, NotifyErrorChanged, NotifyItemChanged virtual in view items - Added custom property store in row views - Reordered and simplified API parameter validation
